description:
Located within the highly desirable complex of Gardene, 69/18 Archipelago Street offers an abundance of versatility and space. Spread across two levels, this ultra-modern townhouse has 3 spacious bedrooms, open plan living/dining area and a private courtyard which provides the perfect space to wind down of an evening. This architecturally designed home is certain to impress from the moment you arrive.

Whether you are looking for your next investment property with a fantastic rental return or are a family looking to settle into an outstanding home, this is a property you don't want to miss out on!
Property features include:

- 3 spacious bedrooms with built in robes
- Master with walk in robe and ensuite
- Generous main bathroom with shower and deep bathtub
- Separate powder room downstairs
- Open plan dining and living area
- Sleek modern kitchen with granite bench tops, gas cooktop and stainless- steel appliances
- An abundance of kitchen storage
- Low maintenance, fully fenced courtyard
- Single car garage with plenty of visitors parking nearby
- Air conditioning and ceiling fans throughout
- Internal floor plan is 131m2 approx.
- Rental appraisal is between $650.00 - $670.00 per week approx.
- Low body corp fees
- Complex has on-site manager, pool & BBQ facilities
- Situated in a secure, gated complex
- Currently tenanted until March 2023

This well managed complex is situated in the heart of Pacific Pines and is only walking distance to local shopping centres, gym & tavern, Pacific Pines Primary & High Schools, transport, and amenities while being a short drive to the M1.

For more information or to book an inspection contact Zoe today!
